Package net.minecraft.nbt

Class CompoundTag

java.lang.Object
net.minecraft.nbt.CompoundTag
All Implemented Interfaces:
Tag
public class CompoundTag  extends Object implements Tag
Represents a NBT Tag that can hold multiple values.
